rket capitalizations the fund invests in stocks of companies that offer products or services or engage in practices that do not violate the core values and teachings of the roman catholic church and does socially responsible investing it employs fundamental analysis focusing on factors such as cash flow earnings dividends book value asset value changes in operations management capital allocation strategies and product offerings to create its portfolio the fund benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the sp midcap  index it does not invest in stocks of companies involved in the practice of abortion distribution of pornographic material those that contribute corporate funds to planned parenthood or those that support embryonic stem cell research the fund was formerly known as schwartz investment trust  ave maria catholic values fund schwartz investment trust  ave maria value fund was formed on may   and is domiciled in the united states detailed description  west ann arbor trailsuite plymouth mi united statesfounded in  phone  fax  avemariafundscomfundsavemxsummaryphp key executives for schwartz investment trust  ave maria value fund mr george peter schwartz cfa portfolio manager mr timothy steven schwartz cfa portfolio manager mr joseph w skornicka cfa portfolio manager compensation as of fiscal year  schwartz investment trust  ave maria value fund key developments ave maria catholic values fund announces portfolio manager changes jan   ave maria catholic values fund announced that timothy s schwartz cfa was named lead portfolio manager joseph w skornicka cfa was named coportfolio manager and george p schwartz cfa remains as coportfolio manager effective january   similar private companies by industry company name region visory llc united states  road partners llc united states t partners llc united states jumpcom inc united states  ontario inc united states recent private companies transactions typedate target no transactions available in the past  month